Tutorial Cloud Foundry Environment in BTP
1. In BTP COCKPIT, go to Entitlements 
2. Click Edit -> Add Service Plans -> Search Cloud Foundry Runtime (Done)
3. Go to Services -> Service Marketplace
4. Search Cloud Foundry runtime & open
5. Create Environment
How to Setting Up SAP Cloud Integration (CPI) In SAP BTP 
(https://developers.sap.com/tutorials/btp-integration-suite-nonsapconnectivity-settingup-suite.html, 
https://developers.sap.com/tutorials/api-mgmt-isuite-initial-setup..html#6a9b02f7-830f-495f-8405-a8ed0b483f1c)
1. Go to Services -> Instances & Subscriptions
2. Klik Create
3. Isi pada field Service 'Integration Suite' & plan.
4. Go to Security -> Users -> klik 
